Tree Disease Alert Phytophthora Root Rot
This disease is widespread and common, particularly on poorly drained sites. Diseased roots are discolored and pull apart easily.  Presence of Phytophthora Root Rot can resulting in wilting and death of the entire plant.
Learn how to prevent root rot








